window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gargoyles are meant to be unbreakable, until they aren’t…<br> <br> The devastating attack on the cadets has the academy in lockdown, and with betrayal coming from within our ranks, my circle of trust grows smaller.<br> <br> The only panacea to my grief is the promise of vengeance against the graynite alpha. I’ll need to pass the elite trial and obtain the power needed to take him down.<br> <br> But the path to justice is never smooth, and as more secrets and lies are revealed, I’m forced to realise that everything is about to change.<br> <br> Cam's adventure continues in The Stone Secret. A heart-pounding MF paranormal romance that weaves a tale of fated mates and impossible desires, where dark secrets and forbidden passions collide, and a hidden destiny awaits.</p>"; 
